   "title": "Settlement account balance trend (STRK)",
   "description": "Starknet settlement (saya) accounts \u2014 update_state needs ~18 STRK resource-bounds headroom to pass validation. Accounts configured via STARKNET_SETTLEMENT_ACCOUNTS in the monitoring .env.",
   "gridPos": {
